ght explain recent observations when\nthe electronic, optical, Raman and other properties of graphene-hBN\nheterostructures have been notably altered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Jan 2014 16:30:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Mar 2014 12:31:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-05"}
