in inhomogeneous systems by superposition. The contour integrals for\nthe 3 components of the acceleration vector are explicitely given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2014 09:09:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
